<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 30 Jun 2026 20:57:10 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>天际线</title><link>https://some.pics/6a442da1e5532</link><description>&lt;p&gt;天际线&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Skyline" height="3730" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/hiddenflair/6a442da1e5532.jpg" width="4974"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://hiddenflair.some.pics"&gt;@hiddenflair&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jun 2026 20:57:10 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a4427d603d26</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一杯凉水&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A tall glass of clear liquid with ice and a lime slice garnish sits on a wooden table next to a brick wall. The outdoor patio setting includes blurred chairs in the background." height="3023" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/mihobu/6a4427d603d26.jpg" width="3023"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://mihobu.some.pics"&gt;@mihobu&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jun 2026 20:32:29 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>沿途</title><link>https://some.pics/6a441d458b034</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一路上。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Blue flowers and city grain near a walkway. " height="2000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/6a441d458b034.jpg" width="1127"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jun 2026 19:47:20 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>比布县法院新古典风格</title><link>https://some.pics/6a441c87e483b</link><description>&lt;p&gt;位于梅肯市中心穆尔伯里街601号的比伯县法院是新古典复兴建筑的典范之作。这座由当地建筑师柯伦·R·埃利斯设计、于1924年竣工的建筑，是自1825年以来服务于该县的第四座法院大楼。其宏伟的廊柱、古典的细节与永恒的设计，使其至今仍是梅肯最具标志性的历史地标之一。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Historic red brick courthouse with tall columns and a green dome clock tower under clear blue sky. Flags and decorative wreaths on steps, conveying civic pride." height="3248" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/6a441c87e483b.jpg" width="2436"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jun 2026 19:44:11 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>水迟迟不凉</title><link>https://some.pics/6a4411c6c44b2</link><description>&lt;p&gt;连用水都降不了温。
（最终至少稍微凉了一点，但这张照片已经是让它运行了很多分钟之后拍的）&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A thermometer showing my tap water is 38C (100.4F) " height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/spu/6a4411c6c44b2.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://spu.some.pics"&gt;@spu&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jun 2026 18:58:18 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>